headline: GE HealthCare announces cash dividend for third quarter of 2025
summary: CHICAGO, September 24, 2025--The Board of Directors of GE HealthCare Technologies Inc. (Nasdaq: GEHC) today declared a cash dividend of $0.035 per share of Common Stock for the third quarter of 2025 payable on November 14, 2025 to all shareholders of record as of October 24, 2025.

headline: 1 Nasdaq 100 Stock on Our Buy List and 2 We Avoid
summary: The Nasdaq 100 (^NDX) is home to some of the biggest success stories in tech and growth investing. However, certain stocks in the index face challenges like profitability concerns, rising costs, or shifts in market trends.

headline: Can AI Help Revitalize The Healthcare Sector For Equity Investors?
summary: Artificial intelligence (AI) applications across the healthcare sector are creating an innovative force that can fuel earnings - and equity return potential - for select companies.
